==評價==
===漫畫===
截至2017年1月，單行本已售出超過100萬冊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-01-26/boruto-naruto-next-generations-anime-features-original-story/.111500|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Anime Features Original Story|publisher=Anime News Network|accessdate=2017-06-01|archive-date=2017-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204053100/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-01-26/boruto-naruto-next-generations-anime-features-original-story/.111500|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》完結時，原作者[[岸本齊史|岸本齊史]]曾對[[集英社|集英社]]表態：“對我而言《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》的故事已經完結，我已經不會再畫了，但若一定要畫下去的话，就一定找[[池本幹雄|池本幹雄]]来主筆，不要讓其他人来畫”，並稱讚道“他的天分無可挑剔，畫功方面早已將我超越。”<ref name=southcn>{{cite news|author1=新浪|title=從鳴人到博人，從岸本到池本——火之意志的繼承與傳承_國外新聞_南方網|url=http://cartoon.southcn.com/c/2017-03/29/content_167953225.htm|work=cartoon.southcn.com|access-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519171832/http://cartoon.southcn.com/c/2017-03/29/content_167953225.htm|archive-date=2017-05-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在一次訪談中，岸本提到，希望池本不要被原作束縛住，哪怕將《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》中的角色畫死也可以，別是無謂的死亡就行{{来源请求||time=2021-10-14}}。但是，[[池本幹雄|池本幹雄]]主筆的續作卻一直因畫風和內容與[[岸本齊史|岸本齊史]]的原作極不協調而飽受詬病。<ref name=southcn />

這部漫畫在日本廣受歡迎，其合輯曾多次列入銷量排行榜。發行當週，第一集單行本便售出183413冊。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-06-02/japanese-comic-ranking-may-22-28/.116971|title=Japanese Comic Ranking, May 22–28|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=5 July 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20170707190220/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-06-02/japanese-comic-ranking-may-22-28/.116971|archive-date=7 July 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-12-21/japanese-comic-ranking-december-12-18/.110212|title=Japanese Comic Ranking, December 12–18|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=5 July 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621211815/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-12-21/japanese-comic-ranking-december-12-18/.110212|archive-date=21 June 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-08-10/japanese-comic-ranking-august-1-7/.105241|title=Japanese Comic Ranking, August 1–7|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=5 July 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702091435/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-08-10/japanese-comic-ranking-august-1-7/.105241|archive-date=2 July 2017}}</ref> 此系列已售出超過100萬冊印刷本 {{as of|2017|January|lc=y}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-01-26/boruto-naruto-next-generations-anime-features-original-story/.111500|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Anime Features Original Story|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608044519/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-01-26/boruto-naruto-next-generations-anime-features-original-story/.111500|archive-date=8 June 2017}}</ref> 2017到2018間，成為[[集英社|集英社]]暢銷漫畫第8名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-04-06/manga-with-biggest-1st-printings-from-kodansha-shogakukan-shueisha-2017-2018/.130071|title=Manga With Biggest 1st Printings from Kodansha, Shogakukan, Shueisha: 2017-2018|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=6 April 2018|access-date=6 May 2018|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109020624/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-04-06/manga-with-biggest-1st-printings-from-kodansha-shogakukan-shueisha-2017-2018/.130071|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其第一集單行本在北美也很暢銷；根據 ICv2，該系列漫畫在2017成為最暢銷系列漫畫第6名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-03-03/icv2-releases-list-of-top-10-manga-franchises-in-fall-2017/.128509|title=ICv2 Releases List of Top 10 Manga Franchises in Fall 2017|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=3 March 2018|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303225754/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-03-03/icv2-releases-list-of-top-10-manga-franchises-in-fall-2017/.128509|archive-date=3 March 2018}}</ref> 2018秋季，《慕留人傳》在北美仍位居暢銷漫畫第4名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://icv2.com/articles/news/view/42553/top-10-manga-franchises-fall-2018|title=TOP 10 MANGA FRANCHISES - FALL 2018|work=Icv2|access-date=May 19, 2019|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111003403/https://icv2.com/articles/news/view/42553/top-10-manga-franchises-fall-2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]（ANN）的Rebecca Silverman說儘管《慕留人傳》從未出現在《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》系列中，依舊不減她對該系列的喜愛。她稱讚作者對慕留人的焦慮沒弄得像怨天尤人的青少年，以及佐助決定收其為徒的過程。<ref name=ANN2>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2017-05-30/the-spring-2017-manga-guide/boruto-vol-1/.116744|title=The Spring 2017 Manga Guide Boruto Vol. 1|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170701034504/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2017-05-30/the-spring-2017-manga-guide/boruto-vol-1/.116744|archive-date=1 July 2017}}</ref> ANN的Amy McNulty評價該漫畫一樣能吸引《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》系列的粉絲，並補充巳月雖然只是個小角色，他的支線故事卻補足了他的背景。<ref name=ANN2/> 來自同一網站的Nik Freeman批評其相比他在《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》完結篇的介紹缺乏發展；Freeman還說鳴人跟慕留人在村里惡作劇不能相提並論。然而，Freeman喜歡巳月的背景故事，因為他覺得這沒讓他感到老調重彈。<ref name=ANN2/>The Fandom Post的Chris Beveridge評價更差，不滿其太過專注在鳴人與慕留人間的矛盾以及重覆描述《[[火影忍者劇場版：慕留人|火影忍者劇場版：慕留人]]》的內容，還批評其承接[[岸本齊史|岸本齊史]]作品的成果；但他稱讚鳴人與佐助的關係以及對成年慕留人戰鬥場面的伏筆。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fandompost.com/2016/05/10/boruto-chapter-1-manga-review/|title=Boruto Chapter #1 Manga Review|work=The Fandom Post|date=10 May 2016|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170701055507/http://www.fandompost.com/2016/05/10/boruto-chapter-1-manga-review/|archive-date=1 July 2017}}</ref>

同一網站的Melina Dargis評論單行本第一冊，儘管看過《[[火影忍者劇場版：慕留人|火影忍者劇場版：慕留人]]》，依然期待主角們未來的發展；她也很喜歡巳月的支線故事。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fandompost.com/2017/05/19/boruto-vol-01-manga-review/|title=Boruto Vol. #01 Manga Review|work=The Fandom Post|date=19 May 2017|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820193209/http://www.fandompost.com/2017/05/19/boruto-vol-01-manga-review/|archive-date=20 August 2017}}</ref>Comic Book Bin的Leroy Douresseaux向《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》的老觀眾推薦該系列，解釋新作者如何成功在單行本第一冊中建立起主角們的人設。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto001.html|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Volume 1 manga review|website=Comic Book Bin|date=3 April 2017|access-date=3 April 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420014452/http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto001.html|archive-date=20 April 2017}}</ref>Dargis對該系列想表達的主題感到驚訝，她發現相比《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》，該系列為迎合當代觀眾而選擇親子與科技的議題。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fandompost.com/2017/10/16/boruto-vol-02-manga-review/|title=Boruto Vol. #02 Manga Review|work=The Fandom Post|date=16 October 2016|access-date=18 October 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417222203/https://www.fandompost.com/2017/10/16/boruto-vol-02-manga-review/|archive-date=17 April 2018}}</ref> Douresseaux喜歡慕留人從單行本第二冊就開始的發展，因為這讓讀者更愛這個角色。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto002.html|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Volume 2 manga review|website=Comic Book Bin|date=24 September 2017|access-date=20 October 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417222203/http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto002.html|archive-date=17 April 2018}}</ref> The Fandom Post和Comic Book Bin指出慕留人的故事取得重大進展，因為它讓第一話閃現的未來變為可能，且新主角們與青的第一場死鬥沒有依賴上一代角色。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fandompost.com/2019/09/29/boruto-vol-06-manga-review/|title=Boruto Vol. #06 Manga Review|publisher=Fandom Post|access-date=September 29, 2019|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020004612/https://www.fandompost.com/2019/09/29/boruto-vol-06-manga-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto006.html|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations: Volume 6 manga review|website=Fandom Post|accessdate=March 18, 2021|archive-date=2021-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603105857/http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto006.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 至於更負面的評論，Manga News批評故事依賴鳴人與佐助來對抗反派「殼」組織，並希望接下來慕留人等人接下來的表現能更活躍。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.manga-news.com/index.php/manga/critique/Boruto-Naruto-Next-Generations/vol-10|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations: Volume 10|publisher=Manga News|access-date=October 22, 2020|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120234309/https://www.manga-news.com/index.php/manga/critique/Boruto-Naruto-Next-Generations/vol-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

川木的登場受到讚揚，不僅是對故事線的影響，還有與慕留人間如同以前鳴人與佐助那平行的對立關係。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fandompost.com/2019/12/11/boruto-vol-07-manga-review/|title=Boruto Vol. #07 Manga Review|publisher=Fandom Post|access-date=January 14, 2020|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020004735/https://www.fandompost.com/2019/12/11/boruto-vol-07-manga-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto007.html|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations: Volume 7 manga review|publisher=Comic Book Bin|access-date=January 14, 2020|archive-date=2021-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603045605/http://www.comicbookbin.com/boruto007.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 遊戲設計師松山洋讚揚川木的首次登場，包括他在劇情上的推動及參與的戰鬥橋段。<ref>{{cite tweet|author=Hiroshi Matsuyama|user=PIROSHI_CC2|number=1093767241194041344|date=February 8, 2019|title=『BORUTO ーボルトー』最新7巻。帯にも書かれてる通り『カワキ編』が本格スタートでアクション多目で見所の多い巻。 それにしても表紙がカッコいい。 カワキの耳の正確な描き込みに池本さんの性格が伺える。|access-date=October 20, 2020}}</ref>

===動畫===
动画版亦受到Charapedia的日本本土读者的喜爱，2017年春季最佳新番票选結果第九名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://otakuusamagazine.com/LatestNews/News1/Japanese-Fans-Choose-the-Spring-2017-Anime-Worth-W-8955.aspx|title=Japanese Fans Choose the Spring 2017 Anime Worth Watching|publisher=Otaku USA|date=2017-05-07|accessdate=2017-06-01|archive-date=2017-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170612041808/http://otakuusamagazine.com/LatestNews/News1/Japanese-Fans-Choose-the-Spring-2017-Anime-Worth-W-8955.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>曾有网友将原作《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》戏称为《博人他爸》、《博人他爸疾风传》，以此暗示《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人传]]》的火爆程度。<ref>{{cite web|title=#BorutosDad Is Actually A Thing Now|url=http://comicbook.com/anime/2017/08/26/-borutosdad-actually-a-thing-now/|website=Anime|accessdate=2017-10-23|language=en|archive-date=2017-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023173824/http://comicbook.com/anime/2017/08/26/-borutosdad-actually-a-thing-now/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]的Sam Stewart讚揚《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》著重描繪新世代忍者及其與上一代的差異，也很喜歡大筒木舍人的回歸與瞳術。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/05/25/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-8-the-dreams-revelation-review|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 8: "The Dream's Revelation" Review|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=25 May 2017|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170701060640/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/05/25/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-8-the-dreams-revelation-review|archive-date=1 July 2017}}</ref>Stewart還稱讚奈良鹿代與李梅塔的角色塑造，覺得他們之間的友誼和意外的決鬥都很賞心悅目，並說《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》每集都越來越好看。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/04/20/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-3-metal-lee-goes-wild-review|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 3: "Metal Lee Goes Wild!"|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=20 April 2017|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530210420/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/04/20/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-3-metal-lee-goes-wild-review|archive-date=30 May 2017}}</ref>[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]的品牌經理Victoria Holden與[[IGN|IGN]]的Miranda Sanchez曾就《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》能否在超越《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》的同時保留其精隨的問題進行討論。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/05/25/can-boruto-live-up-to-narutos-legacy|title=Can Boruto Live up to Naruto's Legacy?|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=25 May 2017|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170531212344/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/05/25/can-boruto-live-up-to-narutos-legacy|archive-date=31 May 2017}}</ref>根據[[東京電視台|東京電視台]]，《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》的獲利創下2018年第五名的佳績。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.txhd.co.jp/pdf/180518_kessan.pdf|title=TV Tokyo HD|publisher=TV Tokyo|access-date=19 October 2018|language=ja|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111003822/https://www.txhd.co.jp/pdf/180518_kessan.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]則報導2018年《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》在多國創下收視佳績，尤其在亞洲。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2018-12-27/crunchyroll-reveals-most-watched-anime-worldwide-for-2018/.141376|title=Crunchyroll Reveals Most Watched Anime Worldwide for 2018|work=Anime News Network|access-date=27 December 2018|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111003940/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2018-12-27/crunchyroll-reveals-most-watched-anime-worldwide-for-2018/.141376|dead-url=no}}</ref>UK Anime Network基於《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》展現出《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》所沒有的故事曲線而獲得超越前作的人氣，因而將其列入2019最佳動漫。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uk-anime.net/articles/UKA_Staff_Best_Anime_of_2019.html|title=UKA Staff Best Anime of 2019|website=UK Anime Network|access-date=March 15, 2020|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121175306/http://uk-anime.net/articles/UKA_Staff_Best_Anime_of_2019.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Geek.com的Tim Tomas拿《[[降世神通：珂拉傳說|降世神通：科拉傳奇]]》與《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》比較，因為它們在延續前作主題的同時又有所區別。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.geek.com/culture/what-to-expect-from-viz-media-for-the-next-3000-years-1673964/|title=What To Expect From Viz Media For the Next 3000 Years|website=[[Geek.com|Geek.com]]|date=10 October 2016|access-date=1 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107112130/http://www.geek.com/culture/what-to-expect-from-viz-media-for-the-next-3000-years-1673964/|archive-date=7 November 2016}}</ref>Sarah Nelkin將《[[慕留人-火影忍者新世代-_(動畫)|博人傳]]》比喻為輕快版本的《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》，但Amy McNulty讚揚第13集專注在從第1集就開始鋪墊的副線劇情，因為它的啟示讓整個系列變得更黑暗。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/05/16/230044|title=Boruto Is Basically What Naruto Would've Looked Like if the World Had Been at Peace|last=Nelkin|first=Sarah|date=16 May 2017|website=Anime Now|access-date=18 May 2017|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170612163429/http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/05/16/230044|archive-date=12 June 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episode-13/.118147|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 13|last=McNulty|first=Amy|date=28 June 2017|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=28 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630210717/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episode-13/.118147|archive-date=30 June 2017 }}</ref>Stewart同意McNulty，並評論道該系列已來到故事曲線的第一波高潮。反派的塑造也令評論家印象深刻。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/29/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-13-the-demon-beast-appears-review|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 13: "The Demon Beast Appears!" Review|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=29 June 2017|access-date=4 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702054040/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/29/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-13-the-demon-beast-appears-review|archive-date=2 July 2017}}</ref>[[Polygon|Polygon]]的Allega Frank提到在漫畫與動畫的開頭閃現成年博人與川木戰鬥的未來，川木暗示那時鳴人已經死亡，讓許多粉絲感到擔憂。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2017/4/6/15208858/is-naruto-dead-in-boruto|title=Boruto premiere leaves fans nervous about Naruto's fate|last=Frank|first=Allega|date=6 April 2017|website=Polygon|access-date=4 July 2017|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170408180836/http://www.polygon.com/2017/4/6/15208858/is-naruto-dead-in-boruto|archive-date=8 April 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>該系列在[[東京動畫獎|東京動畫獎]]2017年百大最佳電視動畫中排行80。<ref>{{cite web|url= https://best100.animefestival.jp/finish.html|title= みんなが選ぶベスト100{{sic|nolink=y|Animes}} of 2017|publisher=[[Tokyo_Anime_Award|Tokyo Anime Award]]|access-date=15 March 2018|url-status= live|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171226234658/https://best100.animefestival.jp/finish.html|archive-date= 26 December 2017}}</ref>

評論家亦針對博人的角色塑造給出不同意見。Beveridge稱讚動畫的第一集，認為博人的描繪比在漫畫中更好；其他評論家則喜歡他那向觀眾傳遞正能量的英雄特質。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fandompost.com/2017/04/05/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-01-anime-review/|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode #02 Anime Review|work=The Fandom Post|date=5 April 2017|access-date=2 June 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://archive.today/20170701060415/http://www.fandompost.com/2017/04/05/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-01-anime-review/|archive-date=1 July 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episodes-31-32/.123784|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episodes 31-32|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=8 November 2017|access-date=4 February 2018|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205072430/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episodes-31-32/.123784|archive-date=5 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://manga.tokyo/interview/an-interview-with-chihiro-ikki-the-voice-of-denki-kaminarimon-from-boruto-naruto-next-generations/2/|title=An Interview With Chihiro Ikki, The Voice of Denki Kaminarimon from Boruto: Naruto Next Generations|website=Manga Tokyo|last=Kouchi|first=Kanako|date=January 2018|access-date=15 March 2018|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316023836/https://manga.tokyo/interview/an-interview-with-chihiro-ikki-the-voice-of-denki-kaminarimon-from-boruto-naruto-next-generations/2/|archive-date=16 March 2018}}</ref>評論家對於回歸角色[[宇智波佐助|宇智波佐助]]變得更關心女兒[[宇智波紗羅妲|宇智波紗羅妲]]表示讚揚，並認為這對他們的角色發展大有幫助；<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/08/24/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-21-sasuke-and-sarada-review|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 21: "Sasuke and Sarada" Review|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=24 August 2017|access-date=30 August 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831045904/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/08/24/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-21-sasuke-and-sarada-review|archive-date=31 August 2017|last=Stewart|first=Sam}}</ref>同時也進一步擴展[[宇智波佐助|佐助]]、[[春野櫻|小櫻]]與[[宇智波紗羅妲|紗羅妲]]這個宇智波家庭成員間的聯繫，這是基於他們之間的連結在動畫第二個故事曲線中的刻畫。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/09/06/230036|title=In Boruto, Sasuke Is a Jerk Who Loves His Daughter|website=Anime Now|date=6 September 2017|access-date=6 September 2017|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906182539/http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/09/06/230036|archive-date=6 September 2017|last=Iikura|first=Ken}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/09/15/230004|title=Sasuke & Sakura's Marriage Has a Balance That's Hard to See|website=Anime Now|date=15 September 2017|access-date=15 September 2017|last=Nelkin|first=Sarah|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916010856/http://www.anime-now.com/entry/2017/09/15/230004|archive-date=16 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/09/08/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-23-bonds-come-in-all-shapes-review|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 23: "Bonds Come In All Shapes" Review|last=Stewart|first=Sam|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=8 September 2017|access-date=8 September 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908204431/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/09/08/boruto-naruto-next-generations-episode-23-bonds-come-in-all-shapes-review|archive-date=8 September 2017}}</ref>

